game.name: Torin's Passage (1995) (Sierra On-Line).dosz
game.comment: Installed from Redump-verified CD-ROM: Torin's Passage (USA) During install, make sure to select NO for performing automatic hardware and graphics speed tests Installation options: Audio: Sound Blaster Directory: C:\SIERRA\TORINDOS After install, copy the FRENCH, GERMAN, MOVIE, and PATCHES directories from the CD to the install directory Then copy the files RESMAP.000, RESMDT.000, RESOURCE.AUD, RESOURCE.SFX, and RESSCI.000 from the CD to the install directory Make the following changes to RESOURCE.CFG (no spaces at the end of these lines): Change line 22 to resSfx= C:\ Change line 23 to resAud= C:\ Change line 24 to resMap= C:\ Change line 25 to movieDir= C:\MOVIE Change line 26 to patchDir= C:\;C:\PATCHES Copy the files from the official Torin's Passage patch to the PATCHES directory in the install directory
game.comment_dosc: CPU max year set to 1995 Auto start Configuration files English, French, and German language options Customized .BAT files to start the game in each language
